Product name:

24K Gold Niacinamide Essence

Description:

Sodium Hyaluonate in 24K Gold Nriacinamide Essence is super hydrating, which can make your skin tender and delicate. The combination of 24K Gold and Niacinamide can can densely hydrate, gently care your fragile skin, and present white and glossy skin. Keep using can not only brighten skin tone, but also moisturize.

Feature:

Whitening;
Moisturizing; 
Brighten skin;
Anti-aging;
Hydrate and moisturize;
Keep PH balance.

Usage:

1. Cleaning skin with warm water.

2. Put two to three drops in the palm of your hand and with fingertips apply to face 
and neck.

3.Gently push up and massage until absorbed.
